<dl id="n42011b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42011b">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42011b"> 11(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> penitent weeps / for priests&apos; sins <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n42011b"><li>FW 188.24 </li><li><a href="../../flex/g/lexg.htm#n42011b">2010</a> </li><li><a href="../../flex/g/l39g.htm#n42011b">1939</a> </li><li><ms href="#n42011b">MS BL 47475-72</ms> </li><li>JJA 47:512 <a name="gd9" href="../../FF/fdra/gda.htm#gd9">Usage</a> </li><li> <a href="../../flex/g/gd9.htm#n42011b">Draft: I.7&sect;1.9</a>/2.9</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">Ah! would to God that all the honest girls and women whom the devil entraps into the snares of auricular confession could hear the cries of distress of those poor priests whom they have tempted &mdash; for ever destroyed! &hellip;they would weep over the irreparable loss of their purity &hellip;. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 35</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: See also: <a name="n42007b" href="n42all.htm#n42007b">N42 (VI.B.31):007(b)</a> </mm> </dd></dl>
